casebody.data:
Percival Norman FENTON, petitioner,
v.
UNITED STATES. No. 12-9771. Supreme Court of the United States May 20, 2013.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied. Petitioner allowed until June 10, 2013, within which to pay the docketing fee required by Rule *240838(a) and to submit a petition in compliance with Rule 33.1 of the Rules of this Court.
